    #
    # The digest below is REQUIRED once the URL is off the official host. Left
    # empty, install.sls falls back to its built-in digest for this version --
    # which is the digest of HashiCorp's zip, so a mirror copy that differs by a
    # byte would fail the check for a reason nobody would guess quickly. It is
